<concept id="freshairheaterTraveller" product="Traveller">
  <title>Fresh air Heater - <keyword conkeyref="brand/estate_model_name"
    >Countryman</keyword></title>
  <shortdesc>The heater is used to heat the interior of the vehicle to let
    you drive in comfort during cold weather. It can also be used to defrost the
    windshield. The <keyword conkeyref="brand/estate_model_name"
    >Countryman</keyword> model has a fresh-air heater which ventilates and circulates the interior
    air while it heats.</shortdesc>
