  <conbody>
    <p>The heater works by using hot water from the engine cooling system to warm the air, and uses
      a shutter control and blower to distribute the air through the interior of the vehicle</p>
    <p>
      <note type="note">The heater blower only operates when the engine is switched on.</note>
    </p>
    <p>There are three controls to operate the heater: a control knob, a shutter control lever and a
      blower motor switch.</p>
